title: China sanctions Pelosi, sends 100 warplanes to Taiwan drills
content:
1. China sanctions Pelosi, sends 100 warplanes to Taiwan drills  The Associated Press
  2. China launches ballistic missiles during Taiwan drills - BBC News  BBC News
  3. Taiwan stocks shake off China's military drills to rise 2%; Asia shares trade higher  CNBC
  4. China fires missiles near Taiwan in live-fire drills as PLA encircles island  CNN
  5. White House summons Chinese ambassador for rebuke on Taiwan response  The Washington Post
